OL,3,CGrooming gang leader warned of
OL,4,C'substantial' jail term after pleading
OL,5,Cguilty
OL,7,FThe leader of a Bolton grooming gang
OL,8,Fhas been warned to expect a
OL,9,F"substantial" jail sentence after
OL,10,Fadmitting a string of rape and sex
OL,11,Foffences involving five under-age
OL,12,Fgirls.
OL,14,FAshley Darbyshire changed his plea to
OL,15,Fguilty on the first day of a scheduled
OL,16,Ftrial at Liverpool Crown Court,
OL,17,Fadmitting to a total of 19 offences.
