OL,5,Cguilty
OL,7,FDarbyshire, of Bolton Road,
OL,8,FWesthoughton, is to be sentenced at a
OL,9,Flater date along with eight other
OL,10,Fmembers of the gang, who were
OL,11,Fconvicted of sex offences in February
OL,12,Fafter a three-month trial.
OL,14,FDarbyshire's fellow gang members are
OL,15,Fall in custody. But because he is
OL,16,Frecovering from a stroke and pleaded
OL,17,Fguilty, he was remanded on bail
OL,18,Fsubject to a number of conditions,
OL,19,Fincluding an electronically-monitored
OL,20,Fcurfew between 6am and 6pm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
