OL,7,FBut the judge, Simon Medland KC,
OL,8,Fwarned him: "However, a substantial
OL,9,Fcustodial sentence is inevitable in
OL,10,Fyour case.
OL,12,F"I heard a great deal of evidence in
OL,13,Fthe first trial about your conduct and
OL,14,Fhow it led to other offences in part."
